==Gothic==
===Etymology===
Proto-Germanic ''*mathon'', derived from Proto-Indo-European ''*math-'' used in insect names.  Cognates include Old English [[maþa]], Old High German [[mado]] (German [[Made]]), Old Saxon [[maðo]] (Dutch [[made]]).

